{"tid":1498781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"向一位九龍灣的街坊道謝","createTime":"2019-08-23T13:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T12:17:36.000Z","uid":277873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54ad6b0c0002173a10d7f07f7a045fe8ebd93b1f","tid":1498781,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:42:14.000Z","msg":"單拖出嚟玩人鏈<br />\n遇到一位好好傾既九龍灣街坊<br />\n多謝你陪我傾咗咁耐<br />\n難得大家好多睇法都近似<br />\n希望有朝一日大家能夠係煲底以真面目相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然你無連登帳<br />\n但你話你會睇連登<br />\n希望你會見到<br />\n加油呀<br />\n唔好覺得孤單<br />\n香港仲有好多同路人㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝你生活安好"},{"pid":"bb205e33d52f000c84d7c08dcb18ef37853cc438","tid":1498781,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"輕力一推<br />\n<br />\n你話你年紀應該大過我<br />\n但我幾肯定應該唔係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a8e807b417945f64f01631d5c7990173ab92b6","tid":1498781,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"最後一推<br />\n今日見到咁多同路人好開心<br />\n大家晚安"},{"pid":"23a913e1e7b966337c61f31476a0afb6a9922a37","tid":1498781,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"估唔到私事PO都有人幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝大家"},{"pid":"34755b174cc59da4d3d69f072c1873928ac16dbd","tid":1498781,"uid":320993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"抱歉要到今天才可以回覆你，<br />\n我這兩天才註冊到連登賬戶啊！<br />\n<br />\n想不到你真的會留言给我，十分感動！<br />\n很多謝那天你陪我傾談，分享你的看法。<br />\n<br />\n很高興能夠認識你，<br />\n真的希望可以與你相見！<br />\n <br />\n我常常獨自參加活動，<br />\n如果有天你一個人需要同伴時，可以找我啊！<br />\n<br />\n願你中秋節快樂！<br />\n願民主與自由在香港萬世不朽！<br />\n<br />\nHong"},{"pid":"3c79de711fa756f09da26ab0234d5ce1e98ea219","tid":1498781,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34755b174cc59da4